        IF_YOU_PROCEED_YOUR_RANK_IN_THE_GUILD                                         = 7239,  -- If you proceed, your rank in the [Carpenters'/Blacksmiths'/Goldsmiths'/Weavers'/Tanners'/Boneworkers'/Alchemists'/Culinarians'] Guild will return to that of [craftsman/artisan/adept], and your skill value will revert to the maximum for that level. This procedure cannot be undone, so please consider your decision carefully.
        RENOUNCE_YOUR_RANK_AS_A_NO_RETAIN_YES                                         = 7240,  -- Renounce your rank as a [Carpenter/Blacksmith/Goldsmith/Weaver/Tanner/Boneworker/Alchemist/Culinarian]? No, retain. Yes, renounce.
        YOU_HAVE_SUCCESSFULLY_RENOUNCED_YOUR_STATUS_AS_A                              = 7241,  -- You have successfully renounced your status as a [craftsman/artisan/adept] of the [Carpenters'/Blacksmiths'/Goldsmiths'/Weavers'/Tanners'/Boneworkers'/Alchemists'/Culinarians'] Guild.
        HUH_HAVE_I_MET_YOU_BEFORE_THIS_IS                                             = 7242,  -- Huh? Have I met you before? This is the Culinarians' Guild. As you can guess, it is an association for professional cooks.
        I_UNDERSTAND_YOU_NOT_WANTING_TO_RUSH_INTO                                     = 7243,  -- I understand you not wanting to rush into anything. As you can see, we have to keep a clean kitchen, so it's not the kind of place unauthorized people should hang about in.
        WELL_IT_S_DONE_THEN_LATELY_A_LOT                                              = 7244,  -- Well, it's done, then! Lately, a lot of adventurers have been signing up to learn. Here. Study a little crystal synthesis with this...
        TO_PUT_IT_SIMPLY_CRYSTALS_ARE_SOLIDIFIED_ENERGY                               = 7245,  -- To put it simply, crystals are solidified energy. Crystal synthesis utilizes that energy to cook individual ingredients into a finished dish.
        BUT_IT_S_NOT_AS_EASY_AS_IT                                                    = 7246,  -- But it's not as easy as it looks. If the cook can't visualize the finished product properly, he could fail, wasting all the ingredients in the process.
        SO_YOU_NEED_TO_GAIN_AS_MUCH_PRACTICE                                          = 7247,  -- So you need to gain as much practice as possible. Only the cook who understands the very essence of his ingredients can make truly exquisite cuisine.
        START_WITH_THE_BASICS_AND_GRADUALLY_BUILD_YOURSELF                            = 7248,  -- Start with the basics and gradually build yourself up. If you need the recipes, your fellow guildsmen can tell you how to make delicacies from all around the world.
        PEOPLE_HAVE_TO_EAT_EVERY_DAY_AND_YOU                                          = 7249,  -- People have to eat every day, and you do not have to be a connoisseur to judge what tastes good. So the ones who provide the food for them have to keep on improving their skills, or the diner will go elsewhere.
        HOW_HAVE_YOU_BEEN_TO_TELL_YOU_THE                                             = 7250,  -- How have you been? To tell you the truth, when I see your face, my mouth starts watering and my stomach starts talking... Are you going to make anything for us today?
        IT_S_ABOUT_TIME_YOU_MOVED_ON_TO                                               = 7251,  -- It's about time you moved on to the next culinarian level. Here then... Whip me up %.
        IF_IT_TASTES_GOOD_AND_IS_PRESENTED_WELL                                       = 7252,  -- If it tastes good and is presented well, I'll teach you some new cooking techniques.
        HMM_IT_S_QUITE_WELL_DONE_I_SHALL                                              = 7253,  -- Hmm... It's quite well done. I shall acknowledge you as [an amateur/a recruit/an initiate/a novice/an apprentice]! Good work! But remember, don't neglect the basics if you want to improve.
        OH_NOW_THIS_IS_DELICIOUS_I_SHALL_ACKNOWLEDGE                                  = 7254,  -- Oh... Now this is delicious! I shall acknowledge you as a journeyman! Ha, perhaps we should get you to teach at our ladies' society cooking school!?
        MOST_INCREDIBLE_I_AM_DELIGHTED_TO_ACKNOWLEDGE_YOU                             = 7255,  -- ......Most incredible! I am delighted to acknowledge you as an artisan! Why, you should open your own restaurant!
        YOUR_HARD_WORK_AND_TOIL_HAVE_FINALLY_PAID                                     = 7256,  -- ... Your hard work and toil have finally paid off! I present you with the title of adept! Let us live the joy of cooking together!
        THERE_AREN_T_ENOUGH_WORDS_IN_THE_TARUTARU                                     = 7257,  -- There aren't enough words in the Tarutaru language to describe the exquisite flavor of this scrumptious dish! You've got to tell me what you put in this!
        OH_LOOK_YOU_MADE_ME_MIX_THE_WRONG                                             = 7258,  -- Oh, look...! You made me mix the wrong quantities. If there's something you want, ask the bigwig standing over there.
        HEY_DIDN_T_WE_JUST_GIVE_YOU_SOME                                              = 7259,  -- Hey, didn't we just give you some help a second ago? Trying to double up, eh? Well it won't work, so there!
        HEY_YOU_DON_T_HAVE_ENOUGH_GIL_YOU                                             = 7260,  -- Hey, you don't have enough gil. You're just like that guy. He was always trying to get help off'a me for free.
        ALRIGHT_THEN_CLOSE_YOUR_EYES                                                  = 7261,  -- Alright then, close your eyes...
        I_THINK_YOU_D_MAKE_A_GOOD_IF                                                  = 7262,  -- I think you'd make a good %, if you tried. Here, it's easy...
        REMEMBER_ALL_I_VE_TOLD_YOU_AND_YOU                                            = 7263,  -- Remember all I've told you and you'll go far. Unless you want to go make all kinds of fancy-wancy creative cooking and ruin the traditions we've tried hard to maintain, like someone we all know...
        EXCUSE_MY_ILL_MANNERS_BUT_I_VE_GOT                                            = 7264,  -- Excuse my ill manners, but I've got my hands full. If there's something you want, ask the master chef.
        BEGGING_YOUR_PARDON_BUT_DIDN_T_WE_JUST                                        = 7265,  -- Begging your pardon, but didn't we just help you a minute ago?
        YOU_DON_T_POSSESS_ENOUGH_GIL_I_M                                              = 7266,  -- You don't possess enough gil, I'm afraid. This would cost you even more in San d'Oria and Bastok, by the way. Both the ingredients and wages are higher there.
        NOW_YOU_RE_COOKING_DON_T_BE_SHY                                               = 7267,  -- Now you're cooking! Don't be shy now. Look into my eyes...
        HMM_MAYBE_YOU_D_LIKE_TO_TRY_MAKING                                            = 7268,  -- Hmm... Maybe you'd like to try making %? So jot down my recipe or commit it to memory if you're so inclined.
        THERE_YOU_HAVE_IT_COME_BACK_AND_ASK                                           = 7269,  -- There you have it. Come back and ask again if you forget it, alright?
        I_M_SORRY_BUT_COULD_YOU_PLEASE_NOT                                            = 7270,  -- I'm sorry, but could you please not bother me? You might make me slip up.
