        SORRY_BUT_I_CAN_SEE_YOU_DON_T                                                 = 7272,  -- Sorry, but I can see you don't have enough gil. Perhaps you're a castaway who finally made it back to dry land, and now needs money to get home? Right...that's the oldest line in the book.
