        WELCOME_TO_THE_RARAB_TAIL_HOSTELRY_DEARIE_THE                                 = 9048,  -- Welcome to the Rarab Tail Hostelry, dearie. The warmest warren for rest and relaxation of all our rarab-like friends.
        WINDURST_IS_A_FUN_PLACE_BEST_ENJOYED_BY                                       = 9049,  -- Windurst is a fun place best enjoyed by leaving all your little worries behind, and letting yourself go with the flow of nature's rythm.
        OUCH_I_WAS_ATTACKED_BY_YAGUDO_THE_OTHER                                       = 9050,  -- Ouch... I was attacked by Yagudo the other day, and my wounds still haven't healed.
        I_INTEND_TO_KEEP_RESTING_UP_HERE_IN                                           = 9051,  -- I intend to keep resting up here in Windurst until all my wounds have completely healed. In the meantime, I've left my house in Mhaura in the care of my younger brother.
        WE_MERCHANTS_HAVE_TO_TRAVEL_IN_ORDER_TO                                       = 9052,  -- We merchants have to travel in order to make any real money. Yet, as you well know, there are so many strong monsters out there in the wilderness.
        MERCHANTS_HAVE_TO_BE_AS_STRONG_AS_WARRIORS                                    = 9053,  -- Merchants have to be as strong as warriors in order to survive in this mauthe-doog-eat-mauthe-doog world!
        HELLO_DEARIE_YOU_RE_AN_ADVENTURER_AREN_T                                      = 9054,  -- Hello, dearie! You're an adventurer, aren't you? Mind if old Chamama asks you for a little favor-wavor, luv?
        YOU_SEE_DEARIE_IT_S_ABOUT_OUR_RARAB                                           = 9055,  -- You see, dearie, it's about our Rarab Tail Hostelry's souvenir dish, Rarab Tail Pickles. Do you know of them? They're famous throughout the whole Federation!
        ANYWAY_TO_MAKE_OUR_RARAB_TAIL_PICKLES_WE                                      = 9056,  -- Anyway, to make our Rarab Tail Pickles, we place a whole lot of % into a barrel and weigh the lid down to slowly pickle them.
        NOW_HERE_S_THE_PROBLEM_DEARIE_I_DROPPED                                       = 9057,  -- Now here's the problem, dearie--I dropped the stone we use to weigh the lid down with, and it shattered into pieces.
        IF_POSSIBLE_I_D_LIKE_AN_ADVENTURER_SUCH                                       = 9058,  -- If possible, I'd like an adventurer, such as yourself, to find me another stone that I could use to weigh the pickle barrel's lid down. A smooth, round, heavy stone...
        HELP_CHAMAMA_OUT_OF_HER_PICKLE_YES_LEAVE                                      = 9059,  -- Help Chamama out of her pickle? Yes. Leave no stone unturned. No. Stonewall her.
        WELL_I_GUESS_YOU_RE_A_BUSY_PERSON                                             = 9060,  -- Well, I guess you're a busy person. Don't worry, dearie, I'll ask someone else to help me out. I'll just pay them the reward instead...
        THANK_YOU_FOR_OFFERING_TO_HELP_ME_DEARIE                                      = 9061,  -- Thank you for offering to help me, dearie. Bring me any smooth, round stones you happen to find, and I'll see if any fit the job.
        THE_PERFECT_STONE_HAS_TO_BE_JUST_THE                                          = 9062,  -- The perfect stone has to be just the right weight. Not too heavy and not too light. It might take us several tries to find the right one, but we'll just have to keep at it until we do.
        IF_YOU_BEAR_WITH_ME_UNTIL_WE_FIND                                             = 9063,  -- If you bear with me until we find just the right stone, then I'll give you a fitting little present.
        I_CAN_T_PICKLE_MY_PROPERLY_UNLESS_I                                           = 9064,  -- I can't pickle my % properly unless I have the proper weighing stone to press the barrel's lid down.
        BRING_ME_ANY_SMOOTH_ROUND_STONES_YOU_HAPPEN                                   = 9065,  -- Bring me any smooth, round stones you happen to find, and I'll see if any fit the job. We'll just have to keep on trying, dearie, until we find just the right one.
        SORRY_TO_BE_SUCH_A_NUISANCE_DEARIE_BUT                                        = 9066,  -- Sorry to be such a nuisance, dearie, but could you please try and find me just the right stone for pickling with?
        I_KNOW_IT_SEEMS_OVERLY_FUSSY_BUT_PLEASE                                       = 9067,  -- I know it seems overly fussy, but please understand. These pickles bear the name of my hostelry on them. Their quality affects our store's image.
        HMM_UM_HMM_IT_NEEDS_TO_BE_A                                                   = 9068,  -- Hmm... Um... Hmm... It needs to be a tad heavier...
        IT_S_NO_GOOD_DEARIE_WE_LL_JUST                                                = 9069,  -- It's no good, dearie. We'll just have to find another one!
        HMM_UM_HMM_IT_NEEDS_TO_BE_A_2                                                 = 9070,  -- Hmm... Um... Hmm... It needs to be a teensy-weensy bit bigger...
        IT_S_NO_GOOD_DEARIE_WE_LL_JUST_2                                              = 9071,  -- It's no good, dearie. We'll just have to try another!
        AH_NOW_THIS_IS_MORE_LIKE_IT_JUST                                              = 9072,  -- Ah! Now this is more like it. Just the right size... Just the right weight...
        THANK_YOU_VERY_MUCH_DEARIE_YOU_DID_WELL                                       = 9073,  -- Thank you very much, dearie. You did well, finding such a perfect pickle stone. I'm sure this will ensure the perfection of our prized pickles!
        HERE_THIS_IS_YOUR_REWARD_DEARIE_IT_S                                          = 9074,  -- Here, this is your reward, dearie. It's something I wore back in the old days when I was a traveling performer. Please use it well.
        JUST_THE_RIGHT_SIZE_JUST_THE_RIGHT_WEIGHT                                     = 9075,  -- Just the right size... Just the right weight... Oh, and so smooth and round, too.
        I_M_SURE_THIS_WILL_MAKE_MY_PICKLES                                            = 9076,  -- I'm sure this will make my pickles just perfect. Our customers should be just delighted, dearie.
        OH_DEARIE_YOU_WON_T_BELIEVE_THIS_BUT                                          = 9077,  -- Oh dearie, you won't believe this, but I went and did it again. Do you mind helping out old Chamama again?
        ONCE_AGAIN_I_ACCIDENTALLY_DROPPED_THE_SMOOTH_STONE                            = 9078,  -- Once again, I accidentally dropped the smooth stone you found for my pickle barrel... And it broke into pieces.
        WOULD_YOU_BE_SO_GOOD_AS_TO_FIND                                               = 9079,  -- Would you be so good as to find me another smooth, round stone there, dearie?
        HERE_PLEASE_TAKE_THIS_AS_A_REWARD_USE                                         = 9080,  -- Here... Please take this as a reward. Use it well, dearie.
        WORK_HARDER_WORK_HARDER                                                       = 9081,  -- Work harder! Work harder!
