        RECENTLY_THERE_S_BEEN_A_LOT_OF_STRANGE                                        = 10743,  -- Recently, there's been a lot of strange characters running around Windurst...even more than usual! I just hope that none of them try to steal this special order I'm supposed to deliver, kupo!
        YOU_VE_COME_TO_PICK_UP_THE_ORDER                                              = 10744,  -- You've come to pick up the order? Are you sure you're not one of those strange characters with the hats, kupo? Well, who am I to judge? Here you go, kupo!
        HM_DID_I_FORGET_SOMETHING_NO_YOU_VE                                           = 10745,  -- Hm? Did I forget something...? ...No, you've got the whole order, kupo.
        HAVE_YOU_SEEN_ANY_CRAZY_GOBLINS_RIDING_AROUND                                 = 10746,  -- Have you seen any crazy Goblins riding around on chocobos lately, kupo?
        OH_YOU_DON_T_HAVE_TO_WORRY_THEY                                               = 10747,  -- Oh, you don't have to worry. They probably won't attack you. They're playing a game with us moogles, kupo!
        YOU_SEE_WE_TAKE_THESE_CARDS_AND_BURY                                          = 10748,  -- You see, we take these cards and bury them around the outskirts of town. Then the Goblins go out and try to find them. If they do, they can bring them back to us and exchange them for different prizes, kupo.
