        WE_VE_DIVINED_THAT_THESE_CREATURES_ARE_INVULNERABLE                           = 10783,  -- We've divined that these creatures are invulnerable to normal weapons! And as if that wasn't enough, they're surrounded by a powerful aura that prevents them from being attacked at all, kupo!
