        THANK_YOU_THERE_IS_ONE_THING_YOU_SHOULD                                       = 12130,  -- Thank you! There is one thing you should know...
        THESE_GHOSTS_ARE_A_LITTLE_VAGUE_BUT_THEY                                      = 12131,  -- These ghosts are a little vague, but they were once people too. If they get a good look at you, they'll know you're just wearing a costume...
