        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_SAY_NOTHING_I                                          = 12649,  -- What would you like to say? Nothing. I'm sorry. It's just an animal! We weren't compatible. Take good care of it.
        IS_THAT_SO_I_GUESS_THIS_IS_HARD                                               = 12650,  -- Is that so? I guess this is hard on you too, then. Sorry...
