        WHAT_MARVELS_COULD_POSSIBLY_LIE_IN_STORE_FOR                                  = 14852,  -- What marvels could possibly lie in store for us today? I've heard it being said that today's [creatures/Cardians] have quite the arsenal of abilities at their disposal. This could get heavy, folks!
        ALL_OF_THE_CONTESTANTS_CERTAINLY_APPEAR_TO_HAVE                               = 14853,  -- All of the contestants certainly appear to have quite a bit of steam left in them. Are they holding back? Could they possibly be working in cahoots with one another!?
        IT_SEEMS_AS_THOUGH_THERE_HAS_BEEN_A                                           = 14854,  -- It seems as though there has been a general quickening of pace amongst the participants!
        THERE_S_STILL_PLENTY_OF_RACE_TO_GO                                            = 14855,  -- There's still plenty of race to go, race fans! More than enough time for an awe-inspiring accident or some downright nasty drama!
        AND_IT_LOOKS_AS_THOUGH_THE_CONTESTANTS_HAVE                                   = 14856,  -- And it looks as though the contestants have have settled in and found their groove!
        THE_RACERS_LOOK_TO_HAVE_GOTTEN_THEMSELVES_INTO                                = 14857,  -- The racers look to have gotten themselves into a bit of a rut now. This could make or break the race! Let's see if they can manage to pull through!
        THIS_IS_WHERE_IT_REALLY_PAYS_OFF_TO                                           = 14858,  -- This is where it really pays off to have an edge in endurance over your opponent. Let's see if any contestants have the discipline to save some steam for the home stretch!
        AND_HERE_S_WHERE_WE_GET_DOWN_TO                                               = 14859,  -- And here's where we get down to the nitty-gritty! Let's see if some of our racers can provide a flamboyant finish for us here today!
        AND_THERE_THEY_GO_A_CLEAR_BOOST_IN                                            = 14860,  -- And there they go! A clear boost in speed for the lot of them! But will they have the endurance to maintain their new pace for long?
        I_AM_AT_A_LOSS_FOR_WORDS_FOLKS                                                = 14861,  -- I am at a loss for words, folks! It's just too hard to call! Which racer will Lady Luck see fit to shine upon today!?
        IT_S_PAINFULLY_OBVIOUS_THAT_THOSE_THOROUGHBREDS_HAVE                          = 14862,  -- It's painfully obvious that those thoroughbreds have nothing but the finish line in their sights now! The time for a final spurt is now or never!
        AND_HERE_THEY_COME_DOWN_THE_HOME_STRETCH                                      = 14863,  -- And here they come down the home stretch! How is this one going to end up!?
        YOU_SEE_A_SINGLE_IVORY_VENTURE_ROLL_DIE                                       = 14864,  -- You see a single, ivory venture roll die on the table. There are currently #/# other players wishing to participate.
        WHAT_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_DO_JOIN_TABLE                                          = 14865,  -- What would you like to do? Join table (# gil). Leave. Read manual.
