        WHY_IS_THAT_SUCH_A_BAD_THING_YOU                                              = 15167,  -- Why is that such a bad thing, you ask? By distracting the prince from giving his undivided attention to the princess, these vivacious vixens could ruin the event, kupo.
        THAT_MUST_NOT_BE_ALLOWED_TO_HAPPEN_IF                                         = 15168,  -- That must not be allowed to happen! If the actor in the prince's role threatens towards fickleness, it's your duty to slap him back to reality--literally!
        AND_WE_CAN_T_FORGET_ABOUT_THE_ACTRESS                                         = 15169,  -- And we can't forget about the actress playing the princess, either. She's under a lot of pressure to perform, and is prone to being plagued with severe self-doubt about her feelings towards her co-star, kupo.
        ONLY_WITH_YOUR_MORAL_SUPPORT_COULD_SHE_HOPE                                   = 15170,  -- Only with your moral support could she hope to maintain confidence and perform at her brilliant best. A simple nod would go a long way to reaffirm positive thoughts, while a shake of the head would do wonders to cast out negative ones, kupo!
        AND_GOING_BACK_TO_THE_SCANDALOUS_SEDUCTRESSES_I                               = 15171,  -- And going back to the scandalous seductresses I mentioned earlier, you can prevent them from disrupting this royal rendezvous by turning their attention to you. A wave of the hand should do the trick, kupo!
