        THERE_IS_ONE_SECRET_TO_HUMANITY_S_SUCCESS                                     = 17193,  -- There is one secret to humanity's success: ambition. Imagining a better future, it strives ever onward in search of it.
        HAVING_SEEN_THE_PROMISED_LAND_IT_RAGES_AND                                    = 17194,  -- Having seen the promised land, it rages and struggles each day to become more than it was meant to be.
        AND_IT_CONTINUES_TO_CLAW_ITS_WAY_FORWARD                                      = 17195,  -- And it continues to claw its way forward, even if what it aspires to be does not truly exist.
        ITS_INSATIABLE_AVARICE_DEFINES_IT_MORE_THAN_EVEN                              = 17196,  -- Its insatiable avarice defines it more than even it can possibly realize.
        BUT_I_AM_NOT_A_HUMAN_SUCH_AS                                                  = 17197,  -- But I am not a human such as you. I will be--I must be--an existence far beyond the most grandiose thought of such petty, grasping beings.
        FOR_THAT_IS_WHAT_LIFE_IS_AND_THOSE                                            = 17198,  -- For that is what life is. And those who cannot reach that pinnacle are fated to perish.
        TIME_IS_A_CRUEL_BEAST_WHOSE_SAVAGENESS_CANNOT                                 = 17199,  -- Time is a cruel beast whose savageness cannot be sated.
        EVERY_MAN_WOMAN_AND_CHILD_FEELS_ITS_CLAWS                                     = 17200,  -- Every man, woman, and child feels its claws sinking into their backs, the talons digging ever deeper with each passing day.
        IT_MARCHES_ON_UNSTOPPABLE_IMMATERIAL_AND_UNFORGIVING_AND                      = 17201,  -- It marches on, unstoppable, immaterial, and unforgiving, and all any of us can do is watch it pass.
        I_CLAIMED_EVER_GREATER_POWER_IN_PURSUIT_OF                                    = 17202,  -- I claimed ever greater power in pursuit of my goals until my time, too, ran out.
        ALL_I_WANTED_TO_DO_WAS_PROTECT_MY                                             = 17203,  -- All I wanted to do was protect my countrymen...my homeland...
        AN_ALTERNATE_WORLD_WITH_ALTERNATE_FATES_AND_ALTERNATE                         = 17204,  -- An alternate world, with alternate fates and alternate existences.
        I_GAMBLED_MY_OWN_LIFE_AWAY_TO_PROTECT                                         = 17205,  -- I gambled my own life away to protect the world I called home.
        CAN_YOU_TRULY_SAY_THAT_YOU_ANY_DIFFERENT                                      = 17206,  -- Can you truly say that you [did/would have done] any different?
        I_CHANNELED_MY_LOVE_FOR_MY_HOMELAND_INTO                                      = 17207,  -- I channeled my love for my homeland into power.
        WHEN_I_FELL_BEFORE_YOU                                                        = 17208,  -- When I fell before you...
        DID_IT_MEAN_EVERYTHING_WAS_FOR_NAUGHT                                         = 17209,  -- ...did it mean everything was for naught?
        I_AND_I_ALONE_HAVE_SEEN_THE_TRUE                                              = 17210,  -- I, and I alone, have seen the true nature of things in this world.
        AND_THUS_I_HAVE_LEARNED_WHY_ALL_BEINGS                                        = 17211,  -- And thus, I have learned why all beings that rise must fall.
        THIS_IS_A_BURDEN_WHICH_I_MUST_BEAR                                            = 17212,  -- This is a burden which I must bear and prevent from happening ever again.
        SHOULD_YOU_NOT_UNDERSTAND_WHY_MY_GOAL_IS                                      = 17213,  -- Should you not understand why my goal is pure and just, then you are unworthy of being called human.
        OPEN_YOUR_EYES_AND_WITNESS_THE_TRUTH                                          = 17214,  -- Open your eyes and witness the truth!
        DON_T_LET_IGNORANCE_CLOUD_YOUR_JUDGMENT                                       = 17215,  -- Don't let ignorance cloud your judgment!
        ID_17216                                                                      = 17216,  -- %...
        WHAT_YOU_SEE_BEFORE_YOU_IS_IT_A                                               = 17217,  -- What you see before you--is it a dream, or something else?
        IS_THIS_A_DREAM_WHAT_ELSE_COULD_IT                                            = 17218,  -- Is this a dream? What else could it be? No. It's something more...
        COME_SURELY_YOUR_VISION_CANNOT_BE_THAT_CLOUDED                                = 17219,  -- Come. Surely your vision cannot be that clouded.
        A_KEEN_EYE_AS_ALWAYS                                                          = 17220,  -- A keen eye, as always.
        THE_MINDS_OF_ALL_WHO_HAVE_EXISTED_AND                                         = 17221,  -- The minds of all who have existed--and all who will exist--are as one.
        AS_TOO_ARE_THE_LIGHT_AND_DARKNESS_INHERENT                                    = 17222,  -- As, too, are the light and darkness inherent in the mothercrystals.
        I_NEED_NOT_POINT_OUT_THAT_THE_APPARITIONS                                     = 17223,  -- I need not point out that the apparitions appearing before you are those whose schemes you have foiled.
        AND_THOSE                                                                     = 17224,  -- And those...
        WHO_YOU_ARE_DESTINED_TO_STOP                                                  = 17225,  -- ...Who you are destined to stop.
        I_HAVE_SOUGHT_THEM_OUT_OF_MY_OWN                                              = 17226,  -- I have sought them out of my own volition, hoping to manipulate their essences for my own ends.
        DARK_INFERNAL_FORCES_SERVING_AS_A_COUNTERBALANCE_TO                           = 17227,  -- Dark, infernal forces, serving as a counterbalance to the light you hope to make manifest.
        AND_NOW_IS_THE_TIME_FOR_ME_TO                                                 = 17228,  -- And now is the time for me to fill you with that energy. Come.
        YOU_DON_T_REALLY_EXPECT_TO_SAVE_THE                                           = 17229,  -- You don't really expect to save the world, do you?
        AT_BEST_YOU_MIGHT_BUY_IT_A_FEW                                                = 17230,  -- At best you might buy it a few more phases of the moon.
        EVEN_SHOULD_I_FALL_THERE_IS_A_GRAND                                           = 17231,  -- Even should I fall, there is a grand legion aching to take my place.
        SO_IN_THE_END_ALL_MY_JOURNEYS_HAVE                                            = 17232,  -- So in the end, all my journeys have been utterly without meaning.
        ONE_BY_ONE_THOSE_I_HAVE_TRUSTED_HAVE                                          = 17233,  -- One by one, those I have trusted have fallen. None are left to prop me up when I begin to falter.
        HAHAHA_NONE_KNOW_WHO_I_RRREALLY_AM                                            = 17234,  -- Hahaha...none know who I rrreally am.
        FALSE_PROPHETS_FALSE_WORLDS_FALSE_ADVENTURERS_THE_TRUTH                       = 17235,  -- False prophets. False worlds. False adventurers... The truth is the pain I feel inside.
        EACH_COMBAT_HAS_PREPARED_ME_FOR_THE_NEXT                                      = 17236,  -- Each combat has prepared me for the next...but in the end, it's all worthless. A new age is descending, and it threatens to leave me behind.
        PANDORA_S_BOX_WOX_HAS_BEEN_OPENED_OVERTURNED                                  = 17237,  -- Pandora's box-wox has been opened, overturned, and shaken until nothing remains inside.
        PERHAPS_NOT_EVEN_YOUR_PRECIOUS_WECIOUS_HOPE                                   = 17238,  -- Perhaps not even your precious-wecious hope.
        SOME_CLAIM_THAT_HOPE_IS_WHAT_KEEPS_HUMANITY                                   = 17239,  -- Some claim that hope is what keeps humanity sane in these trying times...yet in reality it is a prison that shuts away the real world.
        NO_MATTER_HOW_DEEPLY_DARKNESS_HAS_PENETRATED_YOUR                             = 17240,  -- No matter how deeply darkness has penetrated your soul...
        NO_MATTER_HOW_MUCH_YOU_WANT_TO_GIVE                                           = 17241,  -- ...no matter how much you want to give up...
        YOU_MUST_NOT_YOU_CANNOT                                                       = 17242,  -- You must not. You cannot.
        HOPE_IS_SOMETHING_SEIZED_NOT_GIVEN                                            = 17243,  -- Hope is something seized, not given.
        WHETHER_SURROUNDED_BY_FRIENDS_OR_WALKING_A_HARD                               = 17244,  -- Whether surrounded by friends or walking a hard road alone...
        THERE_IS_UNSHAKING_VALUE_IN_SEEING_YOUR_PATH                                  = 17245,  -- There is unshaking value in seeing your path to its conclusion.
        YOU_ARE_THE_CULMINATION_OF_ALL_YOUR_EXPERIENCES                               = 17246,  -- You are the culmination of all your experiences.
        EVEN_THOSE_WHO_ARE_GONE_STILL_DEPEND_ON                                       = 17247,  -- Even those who are gone still depend on you.
