        I_SAY_SYMBOLIC_BECAUSE_IT_TURNS_OUT_THAT                                      = 17541,  -- I say symbolic, because it turns out that's all the gesture-westures amounted to--the homunculi were to be called upon in case a great tragedy befell Windurst. Fortunately, we have not had to use them as of yet.
