        I_SUPPOSE_THIS_APOCRYPHAL_TALE_MUST_BE_TAKEN                                  = 17561,  -- I suppose this apocryphal tale must be taken with a grain of saltaru, but Karaha-Baruha certainly seemed to place some stock in it.
