        AND_THEY_RE_PLANNING_ON_TRADING_IT_TO                                         = 17576,  -- And they're planning on trading it to a rich Tarutaru in Windurst for some silly bauble?
        THERE_S_ONLY_ONE_MERCHANT_SUFFICIENTLY_LAVISH_AND                             = 17577,  -- There's only one merchant sufficiently lavish and malicious to barter-warter with them: Honoi-Gomoi in Windurst Waters.
